N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 319.721 - Fluid extract of meat

State Regulations

Fluid extract of meat (e.g., "Fluid Extract of Beef")
shall contain not more than 50 percent of moisture. Notes
